{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"81a7a261d3","title":"在中共河南省委文教部座谈会上的发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af0198facf","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"81a7a261d3"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"},{"id":"fe1627fb41","name":"王惠敏"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aa9e4d373c","type":"title","text":"在中共河南省委文教部座谈会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"70a01eb1d3","type":"authors","text":"河南王惠敏","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"f7c2398326","type":"subtitle","text":"(王惠敏：《奔流》杂志编辑)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"f261182f02","type":"paragraph","text":"补充两点意见：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"50df329241","type":"paragraph","text":"1．希望省委很好重视文学艺术工作，不要过多受到级别限制，城市、农村工作会议我们均未参加，应让我们及早地多接受些新鲜东西。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"9278ac9f84","type":"paragraph","text":"2．关于一花独放问题，音、美工作者意见很多，（创作不只是李准一人），邹宗绪近日要去北京搞专业，音乐会根本无人管，我省如美术专业化，非饿肚不可，请领导上通盘考虑这些问题。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"d6b7c223cf","type":"paragraph","text":"3．感到省的文学艺术部门，省委应拿出时间搞的好一些，剧协、音协无人做工作，“群众艺术”每月二万字，是否能用两个音乐编辑，据说他们时而作辅导，时而作别的，我们想搞文学出版社。“奔流”目前与出版社有矛盾，不印广告，不给搞彩色图。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"a1f3a76f41","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，思想上有点顾虑：提出的这些意见，能否解决问题呢？但希望能真心解决。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"e8d6639987","type":"paragraph","text":" （根据记录整理）","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"},{"id":"6426ca8d80","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3"}],"page":{"id":"25ec026a6e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"81a7a261d3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}